{
  "page": "Bu Gai",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> God-Emperor</span><br />Bu Gai</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nBu Gai, seventeenth of the azure emperors</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/God-Emperor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God-Emperor\">God-Emperor</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Azure_emperors\" title=\"Azure emperors\">Azure emperors</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Bu Gai</b>, seventeenth of the <a href=\"/index.php/Azure_emperors\" title=\"Azure emperors\">azure emperors</a>, is the current <a href=\"/index.php/God-Emperor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God-Emperor\">God-Emperor</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Empire_of_Yi_Ti\" title=\"Golden Empire of Yi Ti\">Golden Empire</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bu_Gai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Gai's seat is located at the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Yin\" title=\"Yin\">Yin</a>, in a palace said to be larger than all of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. His rule is challenged by imperial general <a href=\"/index.php/Pol_Qo\" title=\"Pol Qo\">Pol Qo</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Trader_Town\" title=\"Trader Town\">Trader Town</a>, who claims to be the first of the <a href=\"/index.php/Orange_emperors\" title=\"Orange emperors\">orange emperors</a>. Another pretender is a <a href=\"/index.php/Sorcerer_lord\" title=\"Sorcerer lord\">sorcerer lord</a>, claiming to be the sixty-ninth <a href=\"/index.php/Yellow_emperors\" title=\"Yellow emperors\">yellow emperor</a> despite the fall of that dynasty a thousand years ago, who is exiled to the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Carcosa\" title=\"Carcosa\">Carcosa</a>, far to the east of Yi Ti.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bu_Gai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Bones and Beyond: Yi Ti.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404120231\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.066 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.250 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 528/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11127/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5030/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 466/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 632/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.48 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  243.185      1 -total\n 97.52%  237.155      1 Template:Infobox_monarch\n 96.62%  234.972      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.78%   31.075     14 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.58%    8.708      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.85%    4.508      1 Template:Ref\n  1.16%    2.813      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.56%    1.356      1 Template:References\n  0.35%    0.846      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19651-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404120231 and revision id 311460\n -->\n",
